95b3de6c1742f","tid":1573211,"uid":120772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"453dfee0144400c2711a1fa1a80198c20062c33c","tid":1573211,"uid":140326,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:20:19.000Z","msg":"三輛行走旺角至九龍灣小巴，遭人以「砂糖灌偈油箱」毒招對付，隨時報廢。有小巴組織指出，近年黑幫多以打爛車窗、塞死氣喉等殺傷力「較輕」招數警告司機，而「砂糖灌偈油箱」則是絕跡多年狠辣招數。 <br />\n<br />\n的士小巴權益關注大聯盟主席黎銘洪指出，「砂糖灌偈油箱」是一種古老毒招，近年已幾近絕跡。他稱，砂糖灌入偈油箱後，倘若司機「撻車」，砂糖會滲入全車喉管，凝固變成晶體阻塞喉管，令全車報廢，做不到生意。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">手足動手前記得先偽裝</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:53:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好陰毒"},{"pid":"d456d90b9b048451784e451ad58c5baa532c17ae","tid":1573211,"uid":4693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:55:06.000Z","msg":"得啦呢到唔想知, 唔需要見報<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb12c5e012b5f6b20e126ac97763903d38945fda","tid":1573211,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:59:23.000Z","msg":"街坊唔好搞佢架車啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7334f433ed9f38f744e984e67b05359d321e1d53","tid":1573211,"uid":6980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:00:50.000Z","msg":"【All you need to know about Hong Kong Protests 2019】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1570834\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1570834</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>【國際文宣】<br />\n抗爭英文版懶人包<br />\n請盡量用英文推post<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">share去twitter同reddit</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"6f9bba6e27a42a8e41f4ee20b04e72802f53a14c","tid":1573211,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:03:28.000Z","msg":"福建愛國人士想打倒外國貨,支持國貨,做事手法污糟"},{"pid":"335bd2a054f28fbc39b308564d6c4dcba92105ed","tid":157321